OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry, bright
OL,6,Fwith hazy sunshine this evening. The
OL,7,Frest of the night will be
OL,8,Fpredominately dry, however a few
OL,9,Fshowers may develop across Dumfries
OL,10,Fand Galloway in the early hours.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FA bright, partly cloudy day
OL,13,Fwith hazy sunny spells. Occasional
OL,14,Fshowers will develop and spread
OL,15,Fnortheast through the day, some may be
OL,16,Fon the heavy side.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
