OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FCloudy
OL,6,Fwith a chance of showers or perhaps
OL,7,Fsome longer spells of rain on Friday
OL,8,Fand Saturday. Dry and brighter on
OL,9,FSunday.
